Anything?

55
00:03:58,830 --> 00:04:01,900
There’s no limit in participants
to challenge Hell Road.

56
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:04,030
I want to team up with you.

57
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:05,440
Hell Road?

58
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:07,070
Why do you choose me?

59
00:04:07,070 --> 00:04:10,990
Because we’re not the real degenerates.

60
00:04:10,990 --> 00:04:14,140
You’re here for training, right?

61
00:04:14,730 --> 00:04:16,540
Is there any problem?

62
00:04:20,540 --> 00:04:24,780
If you’re here for training, you must
win at Hell Road to get out of here.

63
00:04:24,780 --> 00:04:28,220
Hell Road toxicated with heinous spirit,
it’s truly menacing.

64
00:04:28,220 --> 00:04:32,490
