68
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:48,040
I know you’re from Hao Tian Tribe.

69
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:50,750
To show my sincerity,

70
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:52,940
I’ll tell you my origin.

71
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:57,850
I’m Hu Liena, from Martial Soul Hall.

72
00:05:00,780 --> 00:05:02,240
My teacher

73
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:05,480
