Martial Soul Hall and Hao Tian Tribe.

77
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:21,200
Collaborating will brings us benefits.
I can reveal one more secret to you.

78
00:05:24,250 --> 00:05:25,850
If one’s able to pass through Hell Road,

79
00:05:25,850 --> 00:05:28,990
he’ll be recognised by one special domain,

80
00:05:28,990 --> 00:05:31,960
namely, the Death God Domain.

81
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:38,030
It absorbs one’s heinous spirit
and tags on his own martial soul.

82
00:05:38,030 --> 00:05:40,240
<i>Death God Domain?</i>

83
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:43,640
<i>Is this the reason why
Father asked me to come here for?</i>

84
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:46,810
Besides, it’ll enhance

85
00:05:46,810 --> 00:05:50,520
according to the growth of
one’s heinous spirit.

86
00:05:51,820 --> 00:05:54,030
How are you so clear about it?

87
00:05:57,580 --> 00:06:03,320
Because I know someone
who possesses this domain.

88
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,240
Could it be...

89
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:21,740
