97
00:07:20,590 --> 00:07:23,720
His winning rating is just below
Asura King and Emissary of Hell.

98
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:26,880
While the others had won 40 matches.

99
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:30,170
Asura King might not be able
to handle them.

100
00:07:32,330 --> 00:07:34,440
<i>Nine of the Great Soul Land Masters
collaborated?</i>

101
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:37,480
<i>As expected,
the 100th match is strenuous.</i>

102
00:07:38,730 --> 00:07:43,420
Terminate Asura King and
let’s challenge the Hell Road together.

103
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:44,990
He’s just merely a Soul King,

104
00:07:44,990 --> 00:07:47,720
