105
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:48,810
Fight!

106
00:08:06,350 --> 00:08:07,690
Got him.

107
00:08:08,330 --> 00:08:11,240
He is protected by
a strong heinous spirit.

108
00:08:17,470 --> 00:08:20,750
Settle him quickly. Stop him
from condensing his heinous spirit.

109
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:47,880
Phoenix Guides Nine Chicks.

110
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:02,360
