114
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:26,890
Only I can defeat Asura King.

115
00:09:29,470 --> 00:09:33,470
Even Hao Tian Hammer can’t resist this,
Meteor Continuous Hammer.

116
00:09:33,470 --> 00:09:36,680
Meteor Hammer, which is formed from
the condensation of soul power?

117
00:09:38,780 --> 00:09:41,290
I wonder how you can counter it.

118
00:10:03,420 --> 00:10:10,750
