Asura King, 100 matches.

121
00:11:03,260 --> 00:11:06,600
It has been decades that Slaughter City
never emerges a strong one.

122
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,350
I never expect both Emissary of Hell

123
00:11:08,650 --> 00:11:10,210
