124
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:43,100
Congratulations to young Asura King.

125
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:11,400
Slaughter King.

126
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:16,360
<i>- I’ve seen this aura on Dad...</i>
- Slaughter King.

127
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:20,060
<i>He must be the Grand Soul Land Master.</i>

128
00:12:21,290 --> 00:12:24,970
