to boost their soul power.

141
00:13:14,090 --> 00:13:18,000
You’re not deeply poisoned.
Stop before you get worse. Take this.

142
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,520
Eat it if you trust me.

143
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:24,030
