within three days.

144
00:13:24,030 --> 00:13:25,820
If you don’t...

145
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:30,880
I do. Please trust me too.

146
00:13:30,880 --> 00:13:34,510
Because we have to get out of here alive.

147
00:13:43,930 --> 00:13:46,410
I’ve bared my heart to you.

148
00:13:46,410 --> 00:13:49,980
But I’ve no idea who you are.

149
00:13:49,980 --> 00:13:51,720
