150
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:54,840
<i>But I can’t tell you I’m Tang San...</i>

151
00:14:08,610 --> 00:14:09,700
My name is

152
00:14:09,950 --> 00:14:12,090
Tang Yin.

153
00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:40,510
