188
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:51,190
They’d be honored to be the sacrifice

189
00:16:51,210 --> 00:16:53,630
of the opening of Hell Road.

190
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:03,980
<i>Those who’ve seen it have...</i>

191
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:52,890
<i>What’s that?</i>

192
00:17:52,890 --> 00:17:56,170
<i>Even my spirit power can’t endure it...</i>

193
00:18:06,350 --> 00:18:09,790
Wish you good luck.

194
