196
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:31,560
Do you feel it’s getting
hotter and hotter?

197
00:20:31,580 --> 00:20:33,210
Those who collaborated
to challenge Hell Road

198
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:34,640
